r"""
Manipulate Sage functions in the notebook

This module implements a manipulate decorator for function in the Sage
notebook.

The controls are:
\begin{itemize}
    \item InputBox -- a input box
    \item Slider -- a slider
\end{itemize}

AUTHOR:
